Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒辦法保護露易茲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在哪用不著妳管
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你...在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方可是魔法護衛隊隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是保護陛下的守備隊長 就算輸了...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是看著天空\N覺得永遠沒辦法回去而傷心流淚而已 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 你在哈魯凱克大陸這段期間就是我的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅要你幫我做雜事 還要你來保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫瓦魯特保護妳不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你是在意打輸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了 你是男孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和瓦魯特結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H760be3\3c&Hffffff&}露易茲{\1c&H751e13\3c&Hffffff}的結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再拖拖拉拉 快要到出航的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼「是嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 是地震嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基修 在後面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是...魔偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 才人他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們好像要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒說原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 我們兩人就能達成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧 船快要出航了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到棧橋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳來做什麼 虎克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來算上次被關的帳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很行嘛 不過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹也是土系的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼都沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我 基修˙德˙古拉蒙 的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況已經那麼糟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 保王派的情況很不樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯比安王國貴族內亂雖然眾所皆知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是叛亂軍其實已經佔領大部分的國土了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對保王派而言 威魯斯皇太子是唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 露易茲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就全滅了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邱爾潔 塔巴莎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人 你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然攻擊也太卑鄙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是更年期的小偷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更年期 我才二{\fs33\fn方正准圆_GBK}十{\r}三歲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 至少有成功拖延時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖延時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個那個 留著鬍子的帥哥在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出航的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很在意那個帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了一整天才找到你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是執著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又突然看到你們在和魔偶打鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩位已經一起離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的 他說其他兩位會回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基修 棧橋在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在再去棧橋也太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我們該搭的船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...船 不是在飛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的 因為阿魯比安是浮游大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮游大陸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當兩個月亮像今晚一樣重疊之時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是阿魯比安最接近這裡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 瓦魯特子爵和露易茲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易茲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛好像聽到才人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然對那個使魔...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是好像聽到聲音而已 請不要誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是開個玩笑 我不是說要保護妳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦魯特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...接受您的求婚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼瓦魯特子爵會丟下我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎克那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎克？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走的時候說了「成功拖延時間」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該不會是 虎克跟子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能確定 但我唯一知道的 就是露易茲很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一班好像是清晨 現在只能等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是虎克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你們不要丟下我...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beldante
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬我未來的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就等我們達成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 威魯斯皇太子的位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 公主交代我到阿魯比安之前不要對任何人說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 那也是妳的任務之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離到達還有一段時間 用這段時間好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了 露易茲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦魯特大人既強壯又溫柔 也不是使魔或平民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是托利斯提因王國的大使 拉˙巴里艾露氏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能和威魯斯皇太子見面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托利斯提因的大使？ 說謊也要找好一點的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那國家的人不可能知道這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是安莉艾塔公主告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安莉艾塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是來找你們的 威魯斯皇太子在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個戒指是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將戒指伸過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個戒指是阿魯比安王家祖傳的風之寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那個是水之寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水和風會形成彩虹 覆蓋王家的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了 大使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是阿魯比安王國的皇太子 威魯斯˙泰達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是安莉艾塔公主的密書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 皇太子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安莉艾塔公主...安莉艾塔公主是不是建議您逃命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴里艾露小姐 大使想知道密書的內容是越權的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是單純的王族與貴族對立
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷根˙企斯塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那組織就是這內亂的幕後黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴族只不過是被他們利用而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於查到了他們的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:14:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身為阿魯比安的王子 必須保護這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要犧牲我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我告訴安莉艾塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇太子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是那封信件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣任務就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易茲 我想請威魯斯皇太子當我們的證婚人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇太子...難道你想在這裡結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇太子應該會很樂意幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼突然...不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都還沒回托利斯提因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 妳是我的...不 是我們 雷根˙企斯塔 需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 好痛 放開我\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷根˙企斯塔 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦魯特 你竟然...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:15:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的露易茲 妳不用想太多 乖乖聽我的就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 我才不要和你結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳逃不掉的 虛無的末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛 無
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新郎 子爵 傑捷克˙法蘭西斯˙德˙瓦魯特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意以始祖布里米爾之名發誓\N 你會尊敬她 愛她 並娶她為妻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘 拉˙巴里艾露公爵三女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易茲˙法朗索瓦茲˙露布朗˙朵拉˙巴里艾露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什麼 我到底在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊敬他 愛他 並以他為夫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:16:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫？ 你在說什麼 我到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發 我發...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 新娘好像有點緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是 那我再問一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意尊敬他 愛他 並以他為夫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 有人把我的身體...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我 發 我發...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易茲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易茲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 咒縛被...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了公主的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見識到了吧 Beldante只要聞過一次\N就不會忘記寶石的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把露易茲還來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛兵 抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 皇太子殿下 是這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦露特大人 你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙...雷根˙企斯塔...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇太子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇太子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你又能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被下令要殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩 費我這麼多功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是虎克的同夥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易茲 過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起征服世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是我認識的瓦魯特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間會讓人改變 妳總有一天也會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.01,0:18:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢玩弄露易茲的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 談不成的戀愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民的你竟然喜歡上貴族的女孩 真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰管它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 沒有什麼平民貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有家 我有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧夥伴 再加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:19:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有的是 身為露易茲的使魔這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把魔法吸收了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦魯特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 戰鬥的不是我 用你的心揮動我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我這招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是敢傷害露易茲的傢伙 我絕對饒不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 三個目的至少達到了兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個是殺了隱匿蹤跡的威魯斯皇太子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個是得到這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一個目的是 露易茲 就是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然得不到就算了 就請妳在這裡消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 拖拖拉拉的話我們會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是公主的信...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易茲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防護領域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣子不可能還活著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易茲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的露易茲 不用擔心 有我陪著
